green friends Grow for me, grow for me, up to the end"},{"s":37.18,"e":47.26,"text":"I'll keep the water, you keep the light Grow for me, grow for me, every day, every night"},{"s":49,"e":53.66,"text":"The mint is in the corner, like it owns the place"},{"s":53.66,"e":59.02,"text":"The fern is all feathers with a tiny stubborn face"},{"s":59.02,"e":68.9,"text":"I talk to the pothos as I pass the sink You curl around the rail like you know what I think"},{"s":68.9,"e":74.74,"text":"Stretch up, stretch up, take your time, new little leaves on the line"},{"s":74.74,"e":83.96,"text":"Grow for me, grow for me, little green friends Grow for me, grow for me, up to the end"},{"s":83.96,"e":93.92,"text":"I'll keep the water, you keep the light Grow for me, grow for me, every day, every night"},{"s":94.88,"e":105.84,"text":"When the week gets heavy and my hands feel cold You keep making new things out of dirt and old"},{"s":105.84,"e":115.84,"text":"One more inch, one more bloom One more reason to fill this room"},{"s":117.26,"e":126.96,"text":"Grow for me, grow for me, little green friends Grow for me, grow for me, up to the end"},{"s":126.96,"e":138.1,"text":"I'll keep the water, you keep the light Grow for me, grow for me, every day, every night"},{"s":138.1,"e":147.44,"text":"Good morning basil, good night jade Stay right here and don't be afraid"},{"s":148.02,"e":155.66,"text":"Grow for me, grow for me, grow for me"}],"duration":157.60000610351562,"source":"whisper","generatedAt":"2026-05-22T02:33:09.684Z","model":"whisper-1"}